---
import SectionKicker from '../ui/SectionKicker.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../ui/SectionHeading.astro';
---

<section class="bg-surface py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 md:px-10 lg:px-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-stretch gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-12 lg:gap-16">
      <div class="relative z-10 h-full">
        <div class="h-full overflow-hidden rounded-[2.4rem] shadow-[0_24px_44px_rgba(62,39,35,0.14)] transition-transform duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517244683847-7456b63c5969?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80"
            alt="Traditional spice handling in a warm artisan setting"
            class="h-full w-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative z-10 h-full rounded-[2.4rem] bg-dough p-8 shadow-[0_18px_36px_rgba(62,39,35,0.08)] md:p-12 lg:p-14">
        <SectionKicker text="Our Legacy" />
        <div class="mt-4">
          <SectionHeading title="A Legacy in Every Grain" align="left" />
        </div>

        <p class="mt-6 font-body text-base leading-relaxed text-clove/78 md:text-lg">
          Vedic Harvest began in 1951 with a singular belief: purity on the plate starts at the source.
          Our family built long-standing relationships with farmers who cultivate spices and grains with
          care, patience, and regional wisdom that cannot be industrialized.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-5 font-body text-base leading-relaxed text-clove/78 md:text-lg">
          Today we continue that promise through mindful selection, hygienic sorting, and small-batch
          packing. Every pack is designed to carry the aroma, color, and nourishment of Indian soil into
          your kitchen, exactly as nature intended.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
